        <source>The <ph id="f0">&lt;ph class=&quot;- topic/ph &quot; conref=&quot;en-us_topic_0000001645659009.xml#ph122067484595&quot; id=&quot;ph1959151418587&quot; idp:conrefpath=&quot;200650494000#EN-US_BOOKMAP_0000001596019118#EN-US_TOPIC_0000001645659009&quot; idp:userph=&quot;true&quot;/&gt;</ph> may prioritize feeding PV power directly into the grid during high electricity price periods at noon based on the time-of-use electricity price policy, rather than using all of it for power generation (if the returns from selling electricity are higher).</source>
